name: Stranded (itch) (Andy Bae)
description:
Note: Web version of the the game may run slow for some computers. Consider downloading the game for a better experience.

Help is on the way but with only 30 missiles left, do you have enough to fend off the ravaging aliens around you?

I guess if we really need to you can scrap ship parts for more ammunition.

Controls:

        WASD/Arrow keys - Movement

        Space/Enter - Shoot missile

Credits:

Programmer/ArtistAndy BaeMusicPatrick De Arteaga
